&lt;li&gt;Dependent on service line, develops, oversees implementation of behavior, treatment, educational, or medication support plans, as applicable. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assists in the modeling and teaching of behavioral or mental health strategies to necessary stakeholders (e.g., staff, providers). &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Trains the managers, DSP leads, etc. on any plans, or individual specific training, when applicable.  &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
